===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-eɪs|-eɪs]]

===Verb===
'''embrace''', '''[[embraces]]''', '''[[embracing]]''', '''[[embraced]]'''

# [[hug]], put arms around
# {{italbrac|metaphorical}} enfold, include

